Fractions of Structural Panel production used in various end uses

All units are percentages and all vectors are numeric.

fsp_1

Format

A data frame with 151 observations of 16 variables:

House.SingFam
Fraction of structural panel production in Single Family Homes
House.Multifam
Fraction of structural panel production in Multi Family Homes
House.MobHom
Fraction of structural panel production in Mobile Homes
Res.Upkeep
Fraction of structural panel production in Total Residential Upkeep and Improvement
New.Nonres.AllRR
Fraction of structural panel production in All Railroads
New.Nonres.Rties
Fraction of structural panel production in Railroad Ties
New.Nonres.Rcar.Repair
Fraction of structural panel production in Railcar Repair
Manu.HouseFurniture
Fraction of structural panel production in Household Furniture
Manu.CommFurniture
Fraction of structural panel production in Commercial Furniture
Manu.OtherProducts
Fraction of structural panel production in Manufacturing and Other Products
Shipping.Tot
Fraction of structural panel production in Shipping
Other.Uses.Tot
Fraction of structural panel production in Other Uses
Other.Industrial.Tot
Fraction of structural panel production in Uses For Other Industrial Products
